{"parse":{"title":"Contrast","pageid":445,"text":{"*":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>2-1-295</b>\n</p><p>(Luminance) Contrast (of an object against its background)\n</p><p>1. Subjective assessment of the difference in luminance of an object and its background.\n</p><p>2. The quotient of the difference between the luminance of an object and the luminance of its background by the luminance of the background.\n</p><p>Symbol: <span class=\"mw-lingo-term\" data-lingo-term-id=\"0d61f8370cad1d412f80b84d143e1257\">C</span>\n</p><p><br>\n<span class=\"mw-default-size\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/dictionary/index.php/File:2-1-295_Contrast_Equation.png\" class=\"mw-file-description\"><img src=\"/wiki/dictionary/images/d/d2/2-1-295_Contrast_Equation.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"81\" height=\"43\" class=\"mw-file-element\"></a></span>\n</p><p><br>\nwhere L1 is the luminance of the background\n</p><p>L2 is the luminance of the object seen against the background.\n</p><p><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<i>Please note that this is the term as it stands in the original <span class=\"mw-lingo-term\" data-lingo-term-id=\"0a1217bfe27a54fc7e55b72fc62c2371\">IALA</span> Dictionary edition (1970-1989)</i>\n<br>\n</p>\n<div class=\"LanguageLinks\">\n<table width=\"100%\">\n<tbody><tr valign=\"top\" style=\"background: #FFFFFF\">\n<td style=\"width: 25px; padding-left: 0em; border-right: 1px solid #aaaaaa;border-left: 1px solid #EEF3E2;border-top: 1px solid #EEF3E2;border-bottom: 1px solid #EEF3E2;\"><span typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/dictionary/index.php/File:25px-Geographylogo.png\" class=\"mw-file-description\" title=\"Languages\"><img alt=\"Languages\" src=\"/wiki/dictionary/images/8/82/25px-Geographylogo.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"25\" height=\"25\" class=\"mw-file-element\"></a></span></td>\n<td style=\"padding: 1px 1em 0; background: #EEF3E2;\">\n<p><b><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">English</a></b>\n<span></span>\n<span></span>\n<span></span>\n<span></span>\n</p>\n</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div><div class=\"mw-lingo-tooltip\" id=\"0d61f8370cad1d412f80b84d143e1257\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition navigation-not-searchable\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition-text\">\n<p>Contrast\n</p>\n</div></div><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition navigation-not-searchable\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition-text\">\n<p>Celsius (previously Centigrade)\n</p>\n</div></div><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition navigation-not-searchable\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition-text\">\n<p>Capacitance\n</p>\n</div></div>\n</div><div class=\"mw-lingo-tooltip\" id=\"0a1217bfe27a54fc7e55b72fc62c2371\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition navigation-not-searchable\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition-text\">\n<p>International Association of Marine Aids to Navigation and Lighthouse Authorities - AISM\n</p>\n</div></div>\n</div>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260616012319\nCache expiry: 86400\nReduced expiry: false\nComplications: []\nCPU time usage: 0.043 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.062 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 60/1000000\nPost\u2010expand include size: 741/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 112/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/100\nExpensive parser function count: 4/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post\u2010expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   12.591      1 -total\n 74.81%    9.419      1 Template:Languages\n 51.23%    6.450      4 Template:Languages/Lang\n 24.24%    3.052      1 Template:IALAFooter\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key wiki_iala_dictionary_1_41:pcache:idhash:445-0!canonical and timestamp 20260616012319 and revision id 7769. Rendering was triggered because: api-parse\n -->\n</div>"},"langlinks":[],"categories":[{"sortkey":"","*":"2.1_Optics_and_Vision"},{"sortkey":"","*":"Alphabetical_Index"},{"sortkey":"","*":"IALA_Dictionary_1970-89_Edition"}]}}